rceBundle.getBundle(...)` fallback\n  - Handles Native Image dynamic class-loading `Error`s with `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(...)`.\n\n- `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/jetty-util/6.1.26/src/test/resources/org_mortbay_jetty/jetty_util/loader-resource.txt`\n- `tests/src/org.mortbay.jetty/jetty-util/6.1.26/src/test/resources/org_mortbay_jetty/jetty_util/loader_messages.properties`\n\nI did not compile or run tests, per your instruction.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bb226eb4281039f0169f4f43a3c2c819d856d7cc898b7a107\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 530, "output": 1306, "cacheRead": 22016, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 23852, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777660968193, "responseId": "resp_0bb226eb4281039f0169f4f428a178819da2556fd8520c05c8"}, "toolResults": []}
